            <li><span class="numbered-list__num">2</span><span class="numbered-list__text"><strong>文字修飾</strong>：草稿語氣較中規中矩。可依照自己的寫作風格調整語句修飾。</span></li>
            <li><span class="numbered-list__num">3</span><span class="numbered-list__text"><strong>銜接與轉折</strong>：可增加更多承上啟下的過渡句，讓文章讀起來更自然。</span></li>
            <li><span class="numbered-list__num">4</span><span class="numbered-list__text"><strong>確認引用</strong>：定稿前請再次核對草稿中標註「根據文章所述」的部分是否與原文相符。</span></li>
          </ol>
